## Mediawiki automation

1. Terraform : For provisioning two instances and attaching them to a elastic load balancer.


2. Ansible : For configuring the VMs and installing mediawiki in a sinle node setup 


Commands to be used for execution :

Move into terraform directory :

-> terraform init

-> terraform plan

-> terraform apply

For deletion :

-> terraform destroy


Move into ansible directory :

-> ansible-playbook -i hosts test.yaml 
